data.description: 'CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS'Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home beckons you with its allure.As you step inside, be greeted by an inviting ambiance that seamlessly blends comfort and modernity. The spacious living area adorned with natural light sets the tone for relaxation and gatherings. The bonus room, a versatile space, offers endless possibilities--an extra bedroom, home office, a cozy den, or even a play area for the kids.Your culinary aspirations come alive in the well-appointed kitchen boasting sleek countertops, contemporary appliances, and ample storage--a haven for the chef in you.Sliding doors lead you to your private backyard sanctuary--a sprawling pool area where relaxation and entertainment merge effortlessly. Imagine basking in the Florida sun or hosting delightful gatherings by the shimmering pool.Equipped with solar panels, a recent roof upgrade, and a newer energy-efficient HVAC system, this home is designed for sustainability and cost efficiency. The new pool pump ensures hassle-free maintenance, allowing you to enjoy the poolside bliss without worry.The three bedrooms provide comfort and tranquility, offering retreats at the end of a long day. The master suite boasts its own ensuite bath, a personal sanctuary for relaxation.Convenience meets charm with this property's proximity to Tyndall Airforce Base, making commuting a breeze while ensuring you're never too far from the heart of the action.Experience the epitome of contemporary living and schedule your viewing today. Your dream home awaits!
